gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 116, Timberwolves 107
gameRecap.excerpt: Denver defeats Minnesota, 116-107. For Denver, Nikola Jokic led the way with 41 points, 11 rebounds, seven assists, and three steals while aided by Jamal Murray (20 points (four 3PM), four rebounds, six assists) in the victory. Anthony Edwards finished with 25 points and four assists with Rudy Gobert adding 13 points, 15 rebounds, and two steals for Minnesota in the losing effort. Denver improves to 56-24, while Minnesota moves to 55-25 with the loss.
